    "originContent": "# fastcompmgr",
    "translatedContent": "# fastcompmgr"
  },
  {
    "row": 2,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 3,
    "rowsha": "cA5gfA7h3pOIyy7xp/vX4XZqEkm+jlBJ+fnFQDjKqng=",
    "originContent": "__fastcompmgr__ is a _fast_ compositor for X, a fork of an early version",
    "translatedContent": "__fastcompmgr__ es un compositor _rápido_ para X, un fork de una versión temprana"
  },
  {
    "row": 4,
    "rowsha": "FUT6yUto8/ljmqw9tUBzVl030AABYWB0Diw59gZFi1U=",
    "originContent": "of __Compton__ which is a fork of __xcompmgr-dana__ which is a fork",
    "translatedContent": "de __Compton__ que es un fork de __xcompmgr-dana__ que es un fork"
  },
  {
    "row": 5,
    "rowsha": "HVZ+aZsHmCzo4XZxke9MgHB41BTWllNjvy/DKFClhB0=",
    "originContent": "of __xcompmgr__.",
    "translatedContent": "de __xcompmgr__."
  },
  {
    "row": 6,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 7,
    "rowsha": "fRQZaKXUWvbQAcLsWI56/IpXCklXHMaod/dNr5wCFLs=",
    "originContent": "I used to use good old xcompmgr for long, because compton always",
    "translatedContent": "Solía usar el buen y viejo xcompmgr por mucho tiempo, porque compton siempre"
  },
  {
    "row": 8,
    "rowsha": "TauXmdNV2YqgjdeHhqsgOEO/bg+Uk90UD8HnSnXzl6k=",
    "originContent": "felt a bit laggy when moving/resizing windows or kinetic-scrolling",
    "translatedContent": "se sentía un poco lento al mover/redimensionar ventanas o hacer scroll cinético"
  },
  {
    "row": 9,
    "rowsha": "I7Sg12xozTGGVwJILdTdfgYsClawxP4R7aT3DGlCf5s=",
    "originContent": "a webpage. Having tested the latest picom-10.2, it seems, things got even",
    "translatedContent": "en una página web. Habiendo probado el último picom-10.2, parece que las cosas empeoraron"
  },
  {
    "row": 10,
    "rowsha": "FlobFnHyIm8fhuyNqYHs15C0r6/Sq3jpgYo5cZOXhRw=",
    "originContent": "worse (see benchmark below). However, xcompmgr does not draw shadows",
    "translatedContent": "(a ver el benchmark abajo). Sin embargo, xcompmgr no dibuja sombras"
  },
  {
    "row": 11,
    "rowsha": "B+0d9k5wcsokts25WIGNe5qmrT9dezXx225HlBpgtDs=",
    "originContent": "on argb windows (e.g. some terminals) and",
    "translatedContent": "en ventanas argb (por ejemplo, algunos terminales) y"
  },
  {
    "row": 12,
    "rowsha": "OZxJ7Tcv6R3cZOY3rHZMWzTPIDa6cUe748397xsDKFc=",
    "originContent": "has several other glitches. That's why I traveled back into 2011, where",
    "translatedContent": "tiene varios otros fallos. Por eso viajé de regreso a 2011, cuando"
  },
  {
    "row": 13,
    "rowsha": "oRn5TkcETPrUfTeoHoR4EHx/SVQdFBA/+P1D8b7et+M=",
    "originContent": "this feature was just added, cherry picked some later compton commits",
    "translatedContent": "esta característica fue recién añadida, seleccioné algunos commits posteriores de compton"
  },
  {
    "row": 14,
    "rowsha": "JSqZbxHKmKlyTS6RGDrGkMMT+075PpxUJ2QtbDZCu30=",
    "originContent": "to get rid of spurious segfaults and memleaks and made that version even",
    "translatedContent": "para eliminar segfaults y fugas de memoria espurias y hice esa versión aún"
  },
  {
    "row": 15,
    "rowsha": "z/UWEIfpQbBdDAooQidZikM92l1nZWrpU8OAqtyZ92M=",
    "originContent": "faster, based on profiling.",
    "translatedContent": "más rápida, basado en perfilado."
  },
  {
    "row": 16,
    "rowsha": "ipaxbhwwGM7y1BczD7nL39y6K72PHFLNj62d9dUbHfw=",
    "originContent": "For example, window move- and resize events are limited in their",
    "translatedContent": "Por ejemplo, los eventos de mover y redimensionar ventanas están limitados en su"
  },
  {
    "row": 17,
    "rowsha": "86EuETKt9ZoGuo3oedxVww+MX6MdRbJYPjwIs8hNOtA=",
    "originContent": "event-count and rendered at a somewhat fixed framerate, while",
    "translatedContent": "conteo de eventos y renderizados a una tasa de cuadros algo fija, mientras que"
  },
  {
    "row": 18,
    "rowsha": "GdbP4dLIES9DuRd2Pz3+5yOvVk9ilWTJv6Mfj7/Q90s=",
    "originContent": "scrolling is still done as fast as possible. Occluded windows are not",
    "translatedContent": "el desplazamiento sigue siendo tan rápido como sea posible. Las ventanas ocultas no son"
  },
  {
    "row": 19,
    "rowsha": "ApXAtAfl0+6t8/6hpIFKQCW2uFqdcCQMXXlMHOHxcDc=",
    "originContent": "painted and memory allocations/deallocations are largely avoided,",
    "translatedContent": "pintadas y las asignaciones/liberaciones de memoria se evitan en gran medida,"
  },
  {
    "row": 20,
    "rowsha": "BqwQ7sSW0/AcrYIL6We8YYA7df+QzZEybK8lqSOTULY=",
    "originContent": "allowing for faster repaints of the screen.",
    "translatedContent": "permitiendo repintados más rápidos de la pantalla."
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "Q3hzdFXw3i0A2xdOght+uJ6MuxkmlFupzEY6vEDcfVU=",
    "originContent": "On the downside, fading is currently broken (I don't use it). Sorry",
    "translatedContent": "En la parte negativa, el desvanecimiento actualmente está roto (yo no lo uso). Perdón"
  },
  {
    "row": 22,
    "rowsha": "gp5gG6nNhYAwcCd6BOCGTLYAJ6BWM/QKRWvXHTn7k5U=",
    "originContent": "for that (;",
    "translatedContent": "por eso (;"
  },
  {
    "row": 23,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
