    "originContent": "## Benchmark",
    "translatedContent": "## Benchmark"
  },
  {
    "row": 25,
    "rowsha": "GOqcOMlCJugL8NYZ3ir5KtoTnJoKfFko5VSnK1tUk9c=",
    "originContent": "While on my Dell Latitude E5570 window moving, resizing and scrolling",
    "translatedContent": "Mientras en mi Dell Latitude E5570 mover, redimensionar y desplazar ventanas"
  },
  {
    "row": 26,
    "rowsha": "FiHA76o/h9bgV12fRGtEZ/q5o/xArwCgZZCk7PWsqRQ=",
    "originContent": "*feels* clearly faster, there are also some numbers to support this",
    "translatedContent": "*se siente* claramente más rápido, también hay algunos números que apoyan esta"
  },
  {
    "row": 27,
    "rowsha": "2SZVfoS8ApsMzm1MWZCStWnUXavIqt+odV6SSrVLYUU=",
    "originContent": "observation. Given a number of stacked chromium-windows, where no window",
    "translatedContent": "observación. Dado un número de ventanas de chromium apiladas, donde ninguna ventana"
  },
  {
    "row": 28,
    "rowsha": "50LTR9cwbRxQGhuPaQ75fzutRiG4rhuOGvnD6xOs3Zo=",
    "originContent": "is fully occluded, I performed the respective operations *by hand*,",
    "translatedContent": "está completamente oculta, realicé las operaciones respectivas *a mano*,"
  },
  {
    "row": 29,
    "rowsha": "ggLTdjPN/2RU8gNcUv5rPM78gA4Qw/q8svkx9PA+myY=",
    "originContent": "so please beware that the benchmark is not very sophisticated. The touchpad",
    "translatedContent": "así que por favor tenga en cuenta que el benchmark no es muy sofisticado. El driver"
  },
  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "3GSRGkNpjSgmmpU5l6TPbcBVUQxPCNHtv+YXdVGQGrE=",
    "originContent": "driver `xserver-xorg-input-synaptics` was used which enables for kinetic",
    "translatedContent": "del touchpad `xserver-xorg-input-synaptics` fue usado, que habilita desplazamiento"
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
